---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="About Klovo — Made in USA Modular Garage Cabinets"
  description="Klovo is built by Door Kraft — a US cabinet manufacturer with 20 years of experience and over a million cabinets built. Modular garage cabinets, moisture-resistant, furniture-grade, 100% Made in USA."
  keywords="made in USA garage cabinets, American garage cabinets, US-made modular garage cabinets, Door Kraft, Georgia garage cabinet manufacturer"
>

  <!-- Page Hero + Two-column split -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="split">
        <div class="split-text">
          <span class="eyebrow">About Klovo</span>
          <h1 class="page-h1">Garage cabinets,<br/><em>modernized.</em></h1>
          <p class="page-lede">
            Klovo is built by Door Kraft — a US cabinet manufacturer with 20 years of experience and over a million cabinets behind us. We make premium cabinet sets designed for the modern garage: moisture-resistant, furniture-grade, and sized for how people actually use the space today.
          </p>
          <p style="font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 16px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 16px;">
            Our sets are pre-designed, 100% Made in USA, and ship flat for almost tool-free assembly.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="split-media">
          <img
            src="/images/factory/worker-qc.png"
            alt="Klovo quality control — worker inspecting white cabinet panel in the factory"
            style="width:100%; height:auto; display:block;"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pull Quote -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--neutral);">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 760px;">
      <blockquote class="page-pull-quote">
        We didn't pivot to garages. We noticed them.
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Build For -->
  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Our Values</span>
      <h2 class="h-section">What we<br/><em>build for.</em></h2>
      <ul class="page-tick-list" style="margin-top: 40px; max-width: 680px;">
        <li>
          <span class="page-tick">✓</span>
          <div>
            <strong style="font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;">Speed</strong>
            A single cabinet box in about 2–3 minutes. A full set in less than 1 hour. No contractors. No wasted weekend.
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="page-tick">✓</span>
          <div>
            <strong style="font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;">Durability</strong>
            500 lbs per cabinet. 99 lbs per drawer. Moisture-resistant sealed edgebanding. Scratch-resistant laminate. 1-year warranty.
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="page-tick">✓</span>
          <div>
            <strong style="font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;">Accessibility</strong>
            Panels lock together without tools. Push-to-open doors and drawers — no handles needed. Built for every hand and every garage.
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="page-tick">✓</span>
          <div>
            <strong style="font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;">Made in USA</strong>
            Every panel is precision-drilled and sealed in the US. American manufacturing, refined over 20 years.
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Manufacturing Split -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--neutral);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="split" style="align-items: center;">
        <div class="split-media" style="order: 1;">
          <img
            src="/images/factory/cnc-machine.png"
            alt="CNC machine processing white cabinet panels at the Klovo / Door Kraft facility"
            style="width:100%; height:auto; display:block;"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="split-text" style="order: 2;">
          <span class="eyebrow">Made in USA</span>
          <h2 class="h-section">Over a million cabinets.<br/><em>20 years of craft.</em></h2>
          <p style="font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 16px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 20px;">
            Klovo is built by Door Kraft. 20 years of cabinet manufacturing. Precision CNC drilling. Automated PVC edgebanding. Quality control refined through millions of panels.
          </p>
          <p style="font-family: var(--sans); font-size: 16px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 16px;">
            Every Klovo set is inspected, tested, and packed to arrive at your door ready to build.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Band -->
  <section class="page-cta-band">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="color: rgba(244,236,219,0.55);">Ready to Start</span>
      <h2 class="h-final">See what Klovo can do<br/>for <em>your garage.</em></h2>
      <div class="page-cta-btns">
        <a href="/sets/" class="btn btn--primary">View sets &rarr;</a>
        <a href="/where-to-buy/" class="btn btn--ghost btn--ghost--dark">Find a retailer</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</PageLayout>
